{"tid":1175503,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撞車後暫停　港鐵今晚恢復東鐵線新信號測試","createTime":"2019-05-28T14:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T15:42:07.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"645213c9388faaab5b6ac2fb6aaa3b7b99248f16","tid":1175503,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:52:40.000Z","msg":"今年3月荃灣線撞車事故後，港鐵暫停所有新信號系統的行車測試，當中包括東鐵線。港鐵表示，經過全面安全審視，並確認新系統符合測試所需的安全要求後，決定今晚(28日)收車後恢復東鐵線新信號系統的動態行車測試。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵表示，東鐵線的新信號系統與荃灣線的新信號系統不同，港鐵已要求承建商提交詳細報告，再三確定東鐵線新信號系統符合動態行車測試的安全要求。同時，港鐵亦委聘獨立安全顧問作安全評估，確認東鐵線新信號系統符合國際安全標準作動態行車測試。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港鐵指，為確保東鐵線日常列車服務不受影響，測試會安排在每周兩至三晚的非行車時間內進行，期間港鐵會密切監察測試過程，以確保鐵路運作安全，並制訂全面應變措施，減少測試對乘客可能造成的影響。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528163613214-0528_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190528%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190528163613214-0528_00822_001.html&d=AW73mzr4JVDAANnbo7Up2GWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=0b980bcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190528/mobile/bkn-20190528163613214-0528_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a2fbd909bb6a305f0fbb0aac7f89d390d1fb004d","tid":1175503,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"準備撞多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5435464033351adbce0f14296fa14575ec2beba8","tid":1175503,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2fbd909bb6a305f0fbb0aac7f89d390d1fb004d","tid":1175503,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"準備撞多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔同系統供應商 好似係"},{"pid":"f764891778b2068ad18b636cd9d9590376cf9cdb","tid":1175503,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5435464033351adbce0f14296fa14575ec2beba8","tid":1175503,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2fbd909bb6a305f0fbb0aac7f89d390d1fb004d","tid":1175503,"uid":48362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:53:04.000Z","msg":"準備撞多次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T14:57:23.000Z","msg":"唔同系統供應商 好似係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"都可以撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11aff97fedf3e4b7897528614a569481d31a921d","tid":1175503,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"中國世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}